---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const title = "The Ultimate YouTube to MP3 Guide (2026)";
const description = "Learn how to convert YouTube videos to high-quality MP3s safely. Step-by-step instructions, best bitrates (320kbps vs 128kbps), and troubleshooting tips.";
const publishDate = new Date('2026-01-05').toISOString();
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-200 min-h-screen pt-32 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert prose-violet">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-400 to-fuchsia-400 mb-8">{title}</h1>
      
      <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8">
        Converting online video content to offline audio is a staple for music lovers, podcast enthusiasts, and students. In this comprehensive guide, we'll walk you through the fastest, safest ways to extract high-fidelity audio from YouTube and other platforms.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/5 my-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 mt-0">Quick Steps</h2>
        <ol class="space-y-2 text-slate-300 list-decimal pl-5">
            <li><strong>Copy the URL</strong> of the video you want to convert.</li>
            <li><strong>Paste it</strong> into the Convert2MP3 search bar on our homepage.</li>
            <li><strong>Select "MP3"</strong> and choose "High Quality" (320kbps) for the best sound.</li>
            <li><strong>Click Convert</strong> and download your file instantly.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4">Why Bitrate Matters: 128kbps vs 320kbps</h2>
      <p>
        Not all MP3s are created equal. The "bitrate" determines how much data is stored per second of audio.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-slate-400">
        <li><strong>128kbps</strong>: Standard quality. Good for speech, podcasts, or saving data. File sizes are small (~1MB per minute).</li>
        <li><strong>320kbps</strong>: High definition. Essential for music. Preserves the full depth of bass and high-end treble. File sizes are larger (~2.5MB per minute).</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        At Convert2MP3, our "High Quality" setting defaults to the source maximum, often achieving near-320kbps clarity depending on the original uploaded video.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4">Troubleshooting Common Issues</h2>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-violet-400 mt-6 mb-2">"Video Not Found" Error</h3>
      <p>This usually happens if the video is private, age-restricted, or region-locked. Ensure the video is publicly playable in an Incognito window before converting.</p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-violet-400 mt-6 mb-2">Slow Download Speeds</h3>
      <p>Conversion speed depends on the video length and our server load. For long mixes (1 hour+), conversion might take up to a minute. PWA users often experience faster initial connections.</p>

      <!-- Article Schema -->
      <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "Article",
        "headline": title,
        "image": [
            "https://convert2mp3.online/og-image.jpg"
        ],
        "datePublished": publishDate,
        "author": [{
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Convert2MP3 Team",
            "url": "https://convert2mp3.online"
        }]
      })} />
    </article>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
